rows.label: qst102501_msg0001
rows.name: Teacher very late...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0002
rows.name: Friend see teacher Guztin anywhere?

rows.label: qst102501_msg0003
rows.name: Oh...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0004
rows.name:
Teacher left saying was going to
request job of Hræsvelgr Mercenaries.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0005
rows.name:
But no matter how Pilolo wait,
teacher never come back...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0006
rows.name:
Pilolo try asking people from Hræsvelgr
Mercenaries who come to Fons Maim,
but nobody know where teacher go...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0007
rows.name:
Teacher Guztin...
What should Pilolo do...?

rows.label: qst102501_msg0008
rows.name:
Meh-meh?
Friend find teacher for Pilolo?

rows.label: qst102501_msg0009
rows.name: Friend also from Hræsvelgr Mercenaries?

rows.label: qst102501_msg0010
rows.name:
This very lucky meeting!
Pilolo so happy could cry.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0011
rows.name: Oh, Pilolo should clarify details.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0012
rows.name:
Person friend should look for is
teacher called Guztin.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0013
rows.name:
Teacher went to visit village of
Hræsvelgr Mercenaries, but it seem
like never reach village.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0014
rows.name: Pilolo hope friend can find teacher!

rows.label: qst102501_msg0015
rows.name: And hope teacher not hurt or anything...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0101
rows.name: Teacher Guztin is researcher of Divine Beasts!

rows.label: qst102501_msg0102
rows.name:
Plan was to go in Invidia to get
something necessary for Divine Beast research.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0103
rows.name:
Oh, teacher Guztin...
Pilolo hope you are okay...
